drm/amd/display: Correct algorithm for reversed gamma

[Why]
DCN30 needs to correctly program reversed gamma curve, which DCN20
already has.
Also needs to fix a bug that 252-255 values are clipped.

[How]
Apply two fixes into DCN30.

